data.description: Great investor opportunity from motivated seller. Spacious 4 bedroom 3 bathroom ranch home with galley kitchen, large rooms including master bedroom and bathroom.  Large finished basement with full bath and ample storage room.  One of the biggest ranch footprints you will find in the neighborhood.  It has an ample sized backyard with a deck for entertaining and exterior access to the basement.  This home will not last long.
